  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong> and<strong> ginger</strong>, then slice your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>in half lengthways and deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Chop all of these together as finely as you can</p><p>Tip: If you can't handle the heat, save some of the chilli for another recipe!</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619192913395-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619192913395-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619192913395-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619192913395-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619192913395-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic, ginger & chilli</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619192917738-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619192917738-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619192917738-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619192917738-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1619192917738-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> lean beef mince</strong> and your<strong> five-spice mix</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1619192922462-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1619192922462-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1619192922462-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1619192922462-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1619192922462-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lean beef mince is cooking, combine the <strong>cornflour</strong> with 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[100ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[125ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>and give it a good whisk</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tsp]</span> </span><strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>sticky stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1619192931158-x200.jpg",
