          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619192938356-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>medium egg noodles </strong>and<strong> halved Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to a pot and cover with <strong>boiling water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil and cook over a high heat for 5 min or until the noodles are cooked and the broccoli is tender</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>noodles & Tenderstem broccoli</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1619192943802-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1619192943802-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1619192943802-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1619192943802-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1619192943802-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lean beef mince has started to brown, add the <strong>sticky stir-fry sauce </strong>to the pan with<strong> half</strong> the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for 3-4 min or until the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Add the <strong>drained noodles & Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lean</strong> <strong>sticky beef & broccoli noodle stir-fry</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of <strong>starchy</strong> <strong>noodle</strong> <strong>water</strong> if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1619192950129-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1619192950129-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1619192950129-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1619192950129-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1619192950129-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lean</strong> <strong>sticky beef & broccoli noodle stir-fry</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
